{"tid":357844,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"好驚剝牙","createTime":"2017-08-13T09:15:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-13T09:36:18.000Z","uid":3333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8bdf69817601f1ec48466ec0f527babb0328c32d","tid":357844,"uid":3333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T09:15:53.000Z","msg":"唔好牙我老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有隻智慧齒生得好撚入，個位太衰，可能經常有野食zip住既關係。<br />\n越蛀越多，而家食野都要用另一邊黎咬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n朋友話打左麻醉針唔痛，但見人D相，成隻牙連牙肉俾人咁扯出黎真係好鬼驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上年杜過牙根，得覺得剝牙恐怖過杜牙根好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0adedf29024ded3028ae36877128aef035fa3e54","tid":357844,"uid":3333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T09:36:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}